---
/**
 * DiachronicTimeline — Interactive append-only history visualization
 *
 * Embodies: Historia numquam rescribitur; sutura tantum additur.
 *           (History is never rewritten; only a weld is added.)
 *
 * Layers:
 *   1. Ledger stream — F, IC, ω over time (10,023 rows from return_log.csv)
 *   2. Weld events — seam closures with IC_pre → IC_post
 *   3. Version milestones — append-only changelog entries
 *   4. Freeze points — contract snapshots with SHA-256 hashes
 *   5. Epistemic verdicts — RETURN / GESTURE / DISSOLUTION
 */
